&lt;li&gt;Stroke lengths: 25, 50, 75, 100, 125, 150, 175, 200, 250, 300, 350, 400 mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

